General Motors has unveiled the Chevrolet-FNR car was unveiled at the Shanghai General Motors Gala Night this week . 
  It has ‘dragonfly’ swing doors that open upwards and ‘crystal laser headlights’ The car is self-driving, electric and the front chairs can swivel round . 
  Using iris recognition software you can start it using only your eyes . 
  Chevrolet said the car offered a ‘glimpse at mobility of the future’